## 3. Mobs, Zombies & AI

**Goal**: Replace ALL vanilla hostile mobs with 7DTD zombie variants. Vanilla animals partially replaced.

### 3.1 Zombie Variants

| Variant | HP | Damage | Speed (blocks/s) | Special | Spawn Day | Loot |
|---------|-----|--------|-------------------|---------|-----------|------|
| **Walker** | 100 | 8 | 1.0 | Basic, slow | 1+ | Rotten flesh, cloth |
| **Crawler** | 60 | 10 | 0.8 | Low profile, hard to hit | 1+ | Cloth, bones |
| **Frozen Lumberjack** | 150 | 12 | 0.9 | Snow biome exclusive | 1+ | Wood, nails |
| **Bloated Walker** | 200 | 10 | 0.7 | Explodes on death (2-block radius) | 3+ | Rotten flesh, fat |
| **Spider Zombie** | 120 | 14 | 1.8 | Climbs walls, jumps 3 blocks | 5+ | Acid, spider gland |
| **Feral Wight** | 300 | 20 | 2.5 | Always sprints, glowing eyes | 7+ | Iron, mechanical parts |
| **Cop** | 350 | 15 melee, 25 bile ranged | 1.2 | Acid spit (8-block range, 3sec CD), explodes at 20% HP | 14+ | Acid, pistol parts |
| **Screamer** | 80 | 5 | 1.5 | Screams at heat>25 → spawns 4–8 zombies, flees player | 7+ | Cloth, antibiotics |
| **Zombie Dog** | 80 | 18 | 3.5 | Pack spawns (3–5), fast, no climb | 3+ | Bones, animal fat |
| **Vulture** | 60 | 12 | 4.0 (flying) | Dive attacks, hard to hit | 7+ | Feathers, rotten flesh |
| **Demolisher** | 800 | 30 | 1.0 | C4 vest: explodes if chest hit (8-block radius); must headshot | 21+ | Mechanical parts, explosives |
| **Radiated variants** | ×2 HP | ×1.5 dmg | ×1.3 speed | Green glow, regen 2 HP/sec, radiated loot table | 28+ | Rare schematics, advanced parts |
| **Zombie Bear** | 600 | 35 | 2.0 | Charges, AoE swipe | 14+ | Animal fat, bones, meat |
| **Nurse** | 120 | 10 | 1.0 | Heals nearby zombies 5 HP/sec in 5-block radius | 7+ | First aid, painkillers |
| **Soldier** | 400 | 25 | 1.5 | Military loot, higher block damage | 14+ | Ammo, weapon parts |
| **Behemoth** (Boss) | 2000 | 50 | 0.8 | Immune to knockback, AoE ground pound (6-block radius) | 35+ (rare) | Unique schematics, tier 6 items |

### 3.2 Zombie AI System

**Priority-based behavior tree:**
```
Root (Selector)
├── [1] Flee → only Screamer when player within 5 blocks after screaming
├── [2] Attack Target → if player/block in range
│   ├── Melee attack (within 2 blocks)
│   ├── Ranged attack (Cop bile, if >4 blocks)
│   └── Block destruction (pathfind to player, destroy blocks in path)
├── [3] Investigate → move toward heat source / last known player pos
├── [4] Horde Path → during Blood Moon, path to player using A* with block-break cost
└── [5] Wander → random movement within spawn chunk
```

**Pathfinding details:**
- Custom A* implementation with block-break cost function: `cost = baseCost + (blockHP / zombieDamage) × timeMultiplier`.
- Zombies prefer paths through weakest blocks (wood doors > windows > drywall > concrete).
- During Blood Moon, zombies receive global pathing toward nearest player with 64-block scan radius, expanded to 128 on day 21+.
- Spider Zombies add vertical edges (wall climb) to pathfinding graph.
- Group coordination: When 3+ zombies target same block, damage stacks (simulating coordinated bashing).

**Spawning rules:**
- Day: Zombies spawn in dark areas, indoors POIs, underground. Outdoor spawns only biome wanderers (low density).
- Night (18:00–06:00): Spawn rate ×3, all zombies sprint-capable gain +50% speed.
- Blood Moon: Override all spawn rules. Dedicated horde spawner activates.
- Spawn cap: `maxZombies = baseMax + (dayNumber × 2)` capped at config max (default 64 per player, configurable 16–256).

### 3.3 Animals

| Animal | HP | Behavior | Drops |
|--------|-----|----------|-------|
| **Deer** | 80 | Flees on sight (24-block range) | Raw Venison (×3), Bone (×2), Animal Hide (×2) |
| **Rabbit** | 15 | Flees on sound | Raw Rabbit (×1), Bone (×1) |
| **Chicken** | 10 | Wanders, farmable | Raw Chicken, Feather, Egg (if alive, 1/day) |
| **Boar** | 150 | Neutral → hostile if hit | Raw Pork (×4), Animal Fat (×2), Bone (×3) |
| **Wolf** | 120 | Hostile at night, neutral day | Raw Meat (×2), Animal Hide (×3), Bone (×2) |
| **Bear** | 400 | Hostile at 12-block range | Raw Meat (×6), Animal Fat (×4), Bone (×5), Bear Hide |
| **Snake** | 30 | Desert, attacks if stepped on | Venom Sac, Raw Meat (×1) |

