## 5. Skills, Perks & Progression

### 5.1 Attribute System

5 attributes, each level 1–10. Cost: 1 attribute point per level. Points earned every 10 character levels + quest rewards.

| Attribute | Governs | Key Unlocks |
|-----------|---------|-------------|
| **Strength** | Melee damage, carry weight, club/sledge proficiency | Tier 3: Steel tools, Tier 7: Machete master |
| **Perception** | Ranged damage, awareness range, rifle/explosives | Tier 3: Scoped weapons, Tier 7: Sniper headshot bonus |
| **Fortitude** | Health pool, disease resist, healing efficiency, fist/brawling | Tier 3: Iron Gut (no dysentery), Tier 7: Living Off the Land 3 |
| **Agility** | Stamina pool, stealth, movement speed, knives/bows | Tier 3: Parkour (reduced fall dmg), Tier 7: Silent kill bonus |
| **Intellect** | Crafting speed, XP gain, turret damage, better barter | Tier 3: Vehicles unlocked, Tier 7: Max-tier workstations |

